data.description: Lovely Executive home in the sought after Anderson Creek Club Gated Golf Community. Enter Foyer with Formal Dining Room to the right. Primary Suite to the left with sitting area. Primary bath has Jacuzzi Tub and walk in shower with 2 granite top Vanities and 2 walk-in closets. One guest bedroom down with full bath. Straight ahead from Foyer you enter the Great Room that looks out onto a screened in porch and additional deck. The Gourmet kitchen is to the right with large bar area that has room for barstools. Counter tops are Granite. There is a breakfast area adjacent to the kitchen. Kitchen has double ovens, refrigerator, microwave, electric cooktop, diswasher and garbage disposal. Upstairs there are 3 additional bedrooms with one bath. One of the bedrooms could be used as a bonus room. Double car garage. 2023 freshly painted, new carpet, new roof. Floors being refinished and primary bath mirrors updated. Pictures do not depict actual color. Home is a must see. PRICE IMPROVEMENT.
